OL,3,CMurder with no motive: Inside the
OL,4,Ctrial of a dad who stabbed his only
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FSimon Vickers tried to convince the
OL,8,Fjury that his daughter Scarlett died
OL,9,Fin a freak and tragic accident.
OL,11,FHe said it was no fault of his that
OL,12,Fthe 14-year-old somehow collided with
OL,13,Fa kitchen knife that he had
OL,14,Faccidentally swiped to the very edge
OL,15,Fof the kitchen counter during an
OL,16,Finnocent play-fight.
OL,18,FBut the forensic evidence in this case
OL,19,Fwas damning from the start.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
