OL,4,Ctrial of a dad who stabbed his only
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FScarlett's mother Sarah Hall was the
OL,8,Fonly witness there that night.
OL,10,FMiss Hall was deeply emotional while
OL,11,Fgiving evidence in Simon Vickers's
OL,12,Fdefence.
OL,14,FShe told jurors that the family of
OL,15,Fthree had been very, very happy and
OL,16,Fhow her partner had never and would
OL,17,Fnever hurt the daughter they had
OL,18,Fcherished.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
