OL,3,CMurder with no motive: Inside the
OL,4,Ctrial of a dad who stabbed his only
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FTragically, Miss Hall described how
OL,8,Fshe had turned around when she heard
OL,9,FScarlett shout "ow", and panicked when
OL,10,Fshe saw blood pooling across her
OL,11,Fdaughter's pyjama top.
OL,13,FSobbing, she said her greatest fear is
OL,14,Fthat the last thing her daughter saw
OL,15,Fwas the panic and terror in her
OL,16,Fmother's eyes.
OL,18,FCrucially though, Miss Hall conceded
OL,19,Fthat her back was turned when the
OL,20,Fknife entered Scarlett's chest.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
