OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FShe accepted that it was only her
OL,8,Fbelief that it must have been an
OL,9,Faccident.
OL,11,FSimon Vickers's defence highlighted
OL,12,Fhow, despite extensive police
OL,13,Fexamination, there was no evidence
OL,14,Fwhatsoever of any conflict in this
OL,15,Ffamily or between Scarlett and her
OL,16,Ffather.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
