OL,3,CMurder with no motive: Inside the
OL,4,Ctrial of a dad who stabbed his only
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FScarlett's phone was studied; there
OL,8,Fwere no messages to friends, no posts
OL,9,Fon social media which even hinted at
OL,10,Fthat she feared her father for any
OL,11,Freason.
OL,13,FThis family was, the court heard,
OL,14,Fnormal and very happy. It no doubt
OL,15,Fmade the jury's deliberations even
OL,16,Fharder.
OL,18,FAs the judge himself said, it is
OL,19,Fimpossible not to feel sympathy for
OL,20,FScarlett's mother in this tragic case.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
