OL,3,CMurder with no motive: Inside the
OL,4,Ctrial of a dad who stabbed his only
OL,5,Cchild
OL,7,FHowever the jury was also reminded
OL,8,Fthat the prosecution did not have to
OL,9,Fexplain why Vickers stabbed his
OL,10,Fdaughter. Nor were jurors to be
OL,11,Fpersuaded by his clear and obvious
OL,12,Fhorror at her death.
OL,14,FThey just had to decide whether Simon
OL,15,FVickers held the knife that night, and
OL,16,Ftoday they decided on majority of 10
OL,17,Fto two that he did.
